<div class="row row-gutter bg-header-blue-opaque p-1p5 ml-0 mr-0">
<div class="col-md-12 text-center">
<h2 class="h0 mb-0">Our Impact</h2>
<p class="text-large">Results delivered in 2024 from ADB projects.</p>
</div>
<div class="col-md-4 text-center">
<h3 class="mb-0 text-spot-alt text-uppercase count-wrapper" id="data-impact-1"><span class="h1 count-up" id="renewable-1900">1,900</span> megawatts</h3>
<p class="h5">Renewable energy capacity installed</p>
</div>
<div class="col-md-4 text-center">
<h3 class="mb-0 text-spot-alt text-uppercase count-wrapper" id="data-impact-2"><span class="h1 count-up" id="ghgreduction-50.2">50.2</span> million tCO<sub>2</sub>e/year</h3>
<p class="h5">Total annual greenhouse gas<br>emissions reduction</p>
<p class="text-smallest">*tCO<sub>2</sub>e = tonnes of carbon dioxide equivalent</p>
</div>
<div class="col-md-4 text-center">
<h3 class="mb-0 text-spot-alt text-uppercase count-wrapper" id="data-impact-3"><span class="h1 count-up" id="access-98.49">98.49</span>%</h3>
<p class="h5">Proportion of population with<br>access to electricity</p>
</div>
<div class="col-md-12 text-center">
<p><strong>Sources:</strong><br><a href="/documents/development-effectiveness-review-2024-report">2024 Development Effectiveness Review</a></p>
</div>
</div>
        
